    <item>
      <title>欧盟表示准备使用所有贸易工具抵御中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/europe-says-ready-to-use-all-trade-tools-to-defend-against-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩表示，如果中国未能提供公平的市场准入，欧盟准备动用一切可用工具来保卫其经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/europe-says-ready-to-use-all-trade-tools-to-defend-against-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 11:34:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，桑切斯的社会主义者将在加泰罗尼亚选举中赢得第一名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sanchez-s-socialists-set-to-win-first-place-in-catalan-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据《世界报》的一项民意调查，西班牙社会党有望在 5 月 12 日的加泰罗尼亚地区选举中轻松获胜，但远未获得多数席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sanchez-s-socialists-set-to-win-first-place-in-catalan-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 11:33:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京在新任期前夕下令进行战术核演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在他第五任期就职前一天，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京下令俄罗斯军队进行涉及战术核武器的作战演习，加剧了他与西方的对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 07:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯向东部城市挺进，袭击乌克兰北部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russian-air-strikes-cause-power-cuts-in-northern-ukraine-regions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯军队在夺取顿涅茨克东部地区具有重要战略意义的城镇恰西夫亚尔的过程中取得了进一步的进展，而导弹和无人机袭击则扰乱了乌克兰北部和东部的电力供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russian-air-strikes-cause-power-cuts-in-northern-ukraine-regions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:14:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在考虑袭击时要求平民离开拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/israeli-military-starts-moving-civilians-out-of-rafah-kan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方已要求平民撤离拉法部分地区，这可能是人们期待已久的对加沙城市发动袭击的前奏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/israeli-military-starts-moving-civilians-out-of-rafah-kan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 04:57:56 GMT</pubDate>
